      <title>南非新政府选前前景看好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/south-african-election-new-government-edges-closer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两周前，南非非洲人国民大会令人震惊的选举结果导致该党 30 年来首次失去议会多数席位，南非最大的政治对手即将达成协议组建新政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/south-african-election-new-government-edges-closer</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 08:06:49 GMT</pubDate>
